(29222, 'V-gone 100 mg 8 f.c. tablets', 'في-جون 100مجم 8 اقراص', '30', '46', 'Sildenafil', 'Amriya', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '100 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
